<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="furthermore-adv">furthermore <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ˌfɜːðə'mɔː(r)/    美 /ˌfɜːrðər'mɔːr/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-moreover">1.★ <strong>而且；此外 (moreover)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The house isn't big enough for us, and furthermore, it's too far from the town.
这所房子对我们来说不够大，另外，它离市区也太远。</p></div></div>